check which driver I use:
lsmod | egrep "nvidia|nouveau"

disabling neuveuo:

insert this into /etc/modprobe.d/blacklist-nouveau.conf:
blacklist nouveau
options nouveau modeset=0

generate new configs:
sudo mkinitcpio -p linux
then reboot

download proper nvidia driver from website, install

urls:
https://www.nvidia.com/en-in/drivers/details/236036/
https://www.nvidia.com/en-in/drivers/
